1 2Dtable 	42_0063_PF80-24Coils-SameCoilDist-WP3fieldvalCGS.tab			t<400?0:(t<500?0.01*(t-400):(t<700?1:(t<800?0.01*(800-t):0)))		-1
#2 2Dtable 	42_0063_PF80-24Coils-SameCoilDist_newelectrode85cm.table	0	1
